                  + '- {"type":"arrow","x":N,"y":N,"points":[[0,0],[120,0]],"strokeColor":"#334155"}  (points are RELATIVE to x,y; the first point is [0,0])\n'
                  + '- {"type":"line","x":N,"y":N,"points":[[0,0],[0,200]],"strokeColor":"#334155"}\n'
